text: Eskilstuna BS is a bandy club in the town of Eskilstuna in Sweden. It was established in 1965 when the bandy sections of Eskilhems BK and VoIF Diana merged. The men's bandy team played in the Swedish top division in the seasons of 1972-1973 and 1977-1978. == References == ==Other websites== *Official website Category:1965 establishments in Sweden Category:Bandy clubs in Sweden
